<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4894059>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 1. Psychotria defretesiana. A, fruiting stem with galled vegetative structures; B, immature fruits; C, pyrene (9.5 × 7 mm) in proximal-oblique view, the preformed germination slits appearing as a mouthlike orifice. Each of the (2–)3–4 dorsal ridges is abruptly narrowed to a linear crest extending to the exocarp. A–B from Takeuchi et al. 24571; C from Takeuchi & Mogea 21578." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4894059/files/figure.png" .

